General Announcement

K-스타트업 그랜드 챌린지 / The K-Startup Grand Challenge 2024

  • Views 1778
  • Writer 글로벌교류센터
  • 작성일 24.06.04

해외 (예비) 스타트업 대상으로 하는 [K-스타트업 그랜드 챌린지] 홍보 안내드립니다.

K-스타트업 그랜드 챌린지는 2016년부터 진행된 프로그램으로, 올해 9년차를 맞이하고 있으며

매년 전세계에서 2,000명 이상 신청하는 스타트업 경진대회입니다.


[2024 K-스타트업 그랜드 챌린지]

- 신청자격 : 외국 국적의 대표자가 운영하는 해외 (예비) 스타트업

- 지원내용 : 액셀러레이팅 프로그램(3개월), 참가지원금(350만원 x 3개월), 데모데이 상금(총 5억 4천만원), 사무공간 등 인프라 지원, 창업비자 취득 지원 등

- 선정규모 : 40개팀

- 신청기간 : ~2024.6.7.(금) 15:00 KST

- 신청 홈페이지 : k-startupgc.org

- 첨부파일 : 공고문 (한글, 영어)


Dear Entrepreneurs and Startups,

The K-Startup Grand Challenge 2024 has finally returned, revamped by KISED (Korea Institute of Startup & Entrepreneurship Development). KISED is a Korean governmental institution that promotes startups of future entrepreneurs by cultivating an entrepreneurial spirit. KISED establishes a tailored support system for each stage of a startup, from infrastructure and commercialization to globalization, in a bid to identify and nurture game-changing startups and to create an innovative startup ecosystem.


Starting this year, the K-Startup Grand Challenge Program begins anew with KISED, providing an improved program and various benefits for global startups. Including free office space in Pangyo Techno Valley, located close to Seoul, the KSGC 2024 provides a free Korean intern, visa acquisition support, a phase-1 participation subsidy of 3.5 million won per month per team, 1-on-1 startup expert mentoring, various seminars, etc.


The 20 teams selected through Demo Day will be joined in the Follow-up Support (Jan. - Apr. 2025) and each receive an additional phase-2 participation subsidy of 3.5 million won per month per team, as well as a 12-million-won fund for commercialization.


Furthermore, the prize money for the top 5 teams has been increased from $270,000 last year to $400,000 this year. The prize money was allocated as follows: KRW 200,000K ($150,000) for first place, KRW 135,000K ($100,000) for second, KRW 95,000K ($70,000) for third, KRW 70,000K ($50,000) for fourth, and KRW 40,000K ($30,000) for fifth.


Are you ready to expand your business into South Korea?

I really hope to meet you here in Korea.


- Application deadline : ~2024.6.7.(Friday) 15:00 KST

- Application link and detailed information : k-startupgc.org

- Attachment : Official announcement (Korean, English)
